(RDMS) CANNOT be used?
A. Microsoft SQL Server
B. Informix
C. DB2 UDB

A. Information Server metadata repository
B. In the file system as a binary file
C. In the file system as a csv file
D. None of the above
Answer: A

A. Append
B. Replace
C. Truncate
D. All of the above
